              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Three targets were prepared by evaporating BaCO(3) onto",
                "2-mum thin Al foils. The Ba content of the carbonate",
                "powder was enriched to 11.8 +-0.2% in 130Ba. Target",
                "thicknesses were measured to be 554.4+- 17.6 mug/cm**2,",
                "698.3+- 21.9 mug/cm**2,989.9+-30.7 mug/cm**2,",
                "respectively."
